= Biography

Yongheng Wang is currently pursuing the Ph.D. degree in Electrical Engineering at [https://www.hku.hk/ The University of Hong Kong]. He received the M.Phil. degree in Electrical Engineering from [https://www.tsinghua.edu.cn/en/ Tsinghua University] in 2024 and the B.Eng. degree in Electrical Engineering from [https://www.scut.edu.cn/en/ South China University of Technology] in 2021. His research interests lie in the control and optimization of power systems.

